[Re-enable Debug Menus [View Note]]
author=punk7890
description=With the code on, press and hold the following button combinations to enable a menu:

*L1 + Start for Level Select (while at the main menu, before selecting a game mode).
*R1 + L1 for Test Menu when the game is first booting up (nothing works here).
*L2 + Start for Object Viewer 1 (while at the main menu, before selecting a game mode).
*R1 + Start for Object Viewer 2 (while at the main menu, before selecting a game mode).
